---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TopBanner from '../../components/TopBanner.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import heroImage from '../../assets/images/hero-image.jpg';
---

<Layout title="Norway - FiNAN">
  <main>
    <TopBanner />
    <Navbar />
    <PageHeader
      title="Norway"
      description="Discover healthcare opportunities in Norway, renowned for its comprehensive welfare system, natural beauty, and commitment to healthcare excellence."
      backgroundImage={heroImage}
      backgroundAlt="Norwegian fjords and mountain landscape"
    />

    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">
            Healthcare in Norway
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Norway offers exceptional opportunities for Filipino healthcare professionals in a country renowned for its comprehensive welfare system, high quality of life, and stunning natural beauty. The Norwegian healthcare system is publicly funded and emphasizes universal access to high-quality care for all residents.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Healthcare professionals in Norway benefit from excellent working conditions, competitive salaries, and comprehensive social benefits. The country's commitment to work-life balance, professional development, and evidence-based medicine creates an ideal environment for career growth and personal fulfillment.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            World-Class Healthcare System
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Norway's healthcare system is organized into four regional health authorities, providing comprehensive services from primary care to highly specialized treatments. The system emphasizes prevention, patient safety, and quality improvement, offering healthcare professionals opportunities to work with advanced medical technology and participate in international research collaborations.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Natural Beauty and Culture
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Living in Norway means access to spectacular fjords, mountains, and the midnight sun. Norwegian culture values equality, environmental stewardship, and outdoor activities, creating a welcoming community for international professionals. The concept of "friluftsliv" (outdoor life) is central to Norwegian culture, promoting work-life balance and connection with nature.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Professional Growth
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Norwegian healthcare emphasizes continuous learning and professional development. Healthcare professionals have access to excellent training programs, research opportunities, and international exchanges. The country's investment in healthcare innovation and technology provides exciting opportunities for career advancement and contribution to global health improvements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>